---
title: Cacio e Pepe Cheese Tortellini with Roasted Cauliflower
description: Cacio e pepe means cheese and pepper in Italian, and usually refers to a simple pasta dish consisting of Parmesan, salt and freshly cracked black pepper. We’re adding extra cheese with cheese-filled tortellini and roasted cauliflower to make this unbeatable pasta dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cacio-e-pepe-cheese-tortellini-9bcb2ce6.jpg
